  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grave Deceiver</strong> is a rogue-like where a corpse swaps places with you in the grave, casting you into hell while it takes your place in the world of the living. Now, you must fight to escape and return home.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚔️ Damage and Attacks:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This category focuses on enhancing your offensive capabilities, increasing damage, speed, and the effectiveness of your attacks, while adding special effects to cause even more destruction to enemies.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack Speed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Damage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piercing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Critical Hit Chance</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/b82401570dec8c5c961160de7b8bd80a.poster.avif?t=1739387091\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/b82401570dec8c5c961160de7b8bd80a.webm?t=1739387091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/b82401570dec8c5c961160de7b8bd80a.mp4?t=1739387091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏃‍♂️ Movement and Mobility:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your agility and ability to move across the battlefield. These upgrades increase your capacity to jump, run, and attack with greater precision.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extra Jumps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump Height</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement Speed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullet Speed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullet Count</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullet Size</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/4e46f8f21752bb4d9ec4c1ad6b679495.poster.avif?t=1739387091\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/4e46f8f21752bb4d9ec4c1ad6b679495.webm?t=1739387091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/4e46f8f21752bb4d9ec4c1ad6b679495.mp4?t=1739387091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>❤️ Health and Healing:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These upgrades focus on improving your survivability. They help restore your health, boost your resistance, and ensure you’re strong enough to face the toughest challenges.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Healing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Life Steal</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Max Health</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Current Health Healing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/b1dc7546f827d8c8a6c03ee3770dd3ea.poster.avif?t=1739387091\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/b1dc7546f827d8c8a6c03ee3770dd3ea.webm?t=1739387091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/b1dc7546f827d8c8a6c03ee3770dd3ea.mp4?t=1739387091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🦇 Special Abilities:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take advantage of the special effects that make your character unique and powerful. These upgrades offer extra perks to face hordes of enemies and wreak havoc on a massive scale.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bleeding</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fragmentation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bat Swarm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throwing Blades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/b4fb6953d041392fe401704514b6ba9c.poster.avif?t=1739387091\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/b4fb6953d041392fe401704514b6ba9c.webm?t=1739387091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2447340/extras/b4fb6953d041392fe401704514b6ba9c.mp4?t=1739387091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
